author: cms-sw
body: As suggested in https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/issues/46002#issuecomment-3055822370, this PR enable running of DEVEL_X IB RelVals under `cmsTraceFunction --startAfterFunction ScheduleItems::initMisc setenv` to see where we call `setenv`
title: Added cmsTraceFunction for DEVEL_X RelVals
